-09-02-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-canal%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</guid><description>Cannal 完美保持Flannel原生的三种模式，扩展支持Calico的BGP、IPIP模式。并且支持网络策略。 参考链接 Calico网络策略确保CNI</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Canal</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI-Calico详细说明</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-09-01-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-calico%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 22:03:12 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 22:03:12 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-09-01-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-calico%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</guid><description>Calico由Tigera维护，是k8s中另一个流行的开源CNI插件。适用于网络性能、灵活性和功率等因素至关重要的环境。 与 Flannel 不同，Calic</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Calico</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI Flannel详细说明</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-31-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-flannel%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2023 21:19:30 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Thu, 31 Aug 2023 21:19:30 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-31-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-flannel%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</guid><description>Flannel由CoreOS开发，是k8s最成熟的开源CNI插件之一。它提供了一个开箱即用的网络模型，旨在实现更好的容器和主机间的网络。 Fl</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Flannel</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI-概念与入门</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 19:10:41 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 19:10:41 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</guid><description>网络架构是 K8S 的一个复杂组件。Kubernetes 网络模型对特定网络功能提出了要求。业界已开发出许多针对特定环境和要求的网络解决方案。 容器网络</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>CNI</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8s网络CNI-常见网络插件说明与横向对比</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 21:11:32 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2023-08-30-k8s%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9Ccni-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8E%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/</guid><description>CNI(Container NetworkInterface)意为容器网络接口，它是一种标准的设计，为了让用户在容器创建或销毁时都能够更容易地配置容器网络。 由Goog</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>CNI</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s基石</category></item><item><title>K8S基石-理解k8s接口CRI、CNI、CSI</title><link>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2020-05-29-k8s%E5%9F%BA%E7%9F%B3-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3k8s%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3cricnicsi/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2020 00:52:19 +0000</pubDate><author>hex-py@gmail.com (Hex)</author><atom:modified>Fri, 29 May 2020 00:52:19 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://hex-go.github.io/posts/kubernetes/2020-05-29-k8s%E5%9F%BA%E7%9F%B3-%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3k8s%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3cricnicsi/</guid><description>引言 Kubernetes 设计初衷是为模块化的云原生应用程序的部署、扩展和管理提供便捷性和灵活性。在 Kubernetes 的背后，有许多关键组件和接口，这些组件协同工作，以确保集群</description><dc:creator>Hex</dc:creator><category>Kubernetes</category><category>Draft</category><category>Kubernetes<